#: ../../faq.rst:862
# 8f9114ae1fda49ddba9aead14f709bfc
msgid "Try temporarily disabling your antivirus program (Microsoft Security Essentials, or Kaspersky or Norton or McAfee or whatever). This is most likely the culprit if the upgrade process is hanging in the middle."
